parameters: Ah, Madame Ecclesia. Bonjour. What brings me the honor of a saint visiting my boulangerie?
Good morning. I am here to see if the banquet for tomorrow’s ceremony is on schedule.
Do you think you will be able to provide everything in time?
Qui, Of course madame Ecclesia. My apprentices have been working all morning to collect le ingrédiants for the meals. Rest assured that the ceremony’s banquet will be fantastique!
That is good to hear. Keep up the good work. I'll look forward to all that delicious food!!
Hahaha. Don’t worry my dear saint. All of the bakery knows you apprécier delicious good food more than anyone in the nation.
Kehehe! What a lovely steal! This'll sell perfectly on the market! Such is a simple
feat for the legendary Robbin Goblin! Those dogs won't even catch m-
Ahem! Mr Goblin, how many times are we going to tell you not to steal!
The Goblin's defeated... but will he be okay?
It's just a scratch... I'll be alright..
Not to worry, here, take this \c[14]Gold\c[0] and buy a \c[10]Red Medicine\c[0] at the Apothecary.
We can't have you injured for tomorrow's ceremony.
I'll be awaiting your return at the Castle.
No... I don't need to visit the weapon shop.
